1 AN ACT concerning
2 Civil Actions – Noneconomic Damages – Personal Injury and Wrongful Death
3 FOR the purpose of repealing certain limitations on noneconomic damages in civil actions
4 for personal injury or wrongful death; and generally relating to noneconomic
5 damages.
6 BY repealing
7 Article – Courts and Judicial Proceedings
8 Section 11–108
